OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FItaly has banned puppy yoga on animal
OL,8,Fwelfare grounds, as the RSPCA calls
OL,9,Ffor the classes to be halted in the UK.
OL,11,FThe events, which involve puppies
OL,12,Froaming around and being handled
OL,13,Fduring yoga classes, have exploded in
OL,14,Fpopularity in recent years.
OL,16,FFrom Made in Chelsea to The Only Way
OL,17,Fis Essex, some of the top reality
OL,18,Fshows have attended these types of
OL,19,Fclasses - with customers paying up to
OL,20,F#40 a session.
