OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FBut found puppies as young as six
OL,8,Fweeks old being denied access to
OL,9,Fwater, sleep and worked for hours at a
OL,10,Ftime during the sessions .
OL,12,FMany have called for puppy yoga to be
OL,13,Fbanned after an ITV News investigation
OL,14,Fin July found the baby dogs were being
OL,15,Fput at "serious risk" in classes,
OL,16,FCorrespondent Dan Hewitt reports
OL,18,FAs well as puppies being picked up and
OL,19,Fhandled when they were resting.
