OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FThe RSPCA and The Kennel Club both
OL,8,Fsaid the classes should be banned
OL,9,Fafter seeing the ITV News
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FThis week, Italy's Ministry of Health
OL,13,Fbanned the practice on animal welfare
OL,14,Fgrounds, stating only adult dogs
OL,15,Fshould take part in order to protect
OL,16,Fthe health of animals and the safety
OL,17,Fof those who attend.
