OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FEsme Wheeler, dog welfare expert at
OL,8,Fthe RSPCA, said: "Sadly, puppy yoga
OL,9,Fhas gained more traction as time has
OL,10,Fgone on, with people thinking that it
OL,11,Fis 'cute' - but the puppies -
OL,12,Fsometimes younger than eight weeks -
OL,13,Fcan be overwhelmed and frightened.
OL,15,F"It can have such a detrimental effect
OL,16,Fon their welfare, but we're really
OL,17,Fworried the popularity of this trend
OL,18,Fis being fuelled by social media.
