OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FUndercover filming at 'Puppy Yoga
OL,8,FEssex' hosted by The Bully Barn,
OL,9,Fshared in July 2023
OL,11,F"Many puppy yoga organisers say the
OL,12,Fclasses help socialise the animals,
OL,13,Fbut socialisation needs to be carried
OL,14,Fout gradually, where exposure to
OL,15,Fvarious experiences, people and other
OL,16,Fanimals is controlled and calm. Not
OL,17,Fdoing so can have a negative effect on
OL,18,Fthe puppy.
