OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,F"We hope the ban on puppy yoga in
OL,8,FItaly sends a strong message to anyone
OL,9,Fconsidering attending one in this
OL,10,Fcountry to stay away."
OL,12,FLast month, a report from the
OL,13,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,14,Fparliamentary committee raised
OL,15,Fconcerns about puppy yoga.
OL,17,FIt said the welfare of underage and
OL,18,Fpotentially unvaccinated puppies in
OL,19,Fthe yoga class setting may be
OL,20,Fdetrimental to their health and
OL,21,Fwellbeing.
