OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,FDr Neil Hudson MP FRCVS, Member of the
OL,8,FEFRA Select Committee and the only
OL,9,Fveterinary surgeon in the House of
OL,10,FCommons said: "It is really welcome
OL,11,Fthat Italy has taken the step to ban
OL,12,Fpuppy yoga. Although it sounds nice
OL,13,Fand benign, this practice often uses
OL,14,Funderage and potentially unvaccinated
OL,15,Fpuppies and raises real concerns for
OL,16,Ftheir health and welfare.
