OL,3,CRSPCA urges government to stop
OL,4,C'frightening' puppy yoga as Italy bans
OL,5,Cclasses
OL,7,F"Our EFRA Select Committee looked at
OL,8,Fthis and made recommendations in our
OL,9,Frecent Report on Pet and Welfare Abuse
OL,10,Ffor the Government to look at
OL,11,Fregulating this or indeed banning the
OL,12,Fpractice.
OL,14,F"The developments in Italy add weight
OL,15,Fto the case for banning this
OL,16,Funacceptable practice here in the UK."
OL,18,FAnyone who has concerns about puppy
OL,19,Fyoga enterprises in their area is
OL,20,Furged to contact their local council,
OL,21,Fthe RSPCA advises.
